                1.34-3 3 1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 
                2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 
                2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v3h16v-3c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4zm8 
                0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05C17.48 13.23 20 14.5 20 16v3h4v-3
                c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
            </svg>
            User Management
